On the 9th February a huge heart will be installed in Camden Lock. 

Members of the public will bring this installation to life by attaching their own individual declaration of love, a love padlock. 

The Challenge Society is taking over the Heart padlocks for a day and we'll be running competitions to see who can raise the most for BHF. 

It is vital that we know who is coming on the day so please RSVP to grace.harris@the-challenge.org or 07584232767. 


So are you up to the Challenge?

The details of where to be when are...

When: Saturday 9th February

Time: 11am-6pm (you can come 11-2.30, 2.30-6 or for the whole day!)
Where: Camden Lock Market, East Yard (the fist part of Camden Market after the bridge

You can also bring any friends along with you who might like to come (between the age of 14 & 19).






 
 
 
	
 
 
 
 
 
 
	
 
 
 
 
 
 
 	
 
 
